rs and tables. Travis\' new backyard also includes a grassy area as well as a patio that spills into the living room on the second floor. One of the most eye-popping features of the house is a dizzying white spiral staircase against a grey metallic banister. Inside, theres also a gym, a games room and a home cinema complete with cushioned cinema-style seats that have cup-holders in the armrests. A huge bar has a gleaming black back wall lined with liquor shelves. Up on the third floor of his house, the hardwood flooring has a stylish three-dimensional cube pattern meant to look like tile. The master bedroom suite has a balcony and an ensuite bathroom with a luxurious bowl-shaped bathtub and a massive shower. A sitting room on the top floor has stunning city views with floor-to-ceiling windows. Travis has a two-year-old daughter called Stormi with his ex Kylie Jenner. The former couple still own a .5 million Los Angeles home. Photo by ABACAPRESS.COM  Maison Villa House  | 734262_031 Los Angekes Etats-Unis United States\";s:17:\"created_timestamp\";s:10:\"1592611200\";s:9:\"copyright\";s:0:\"\";s:12:\"focal_length\";s:1:\"0\";s:3:\"iso\";s:1:\"0\";s:13:\"shutter_speed\";s:1:\"0\";s:5:\"title\";s:58:\"Travis Scott Splashed Out  Million On A Sleek Mansion - LA\";s:11:\"orientation\";s:1:\"1\";s:8:\"keywords\";a:1:{i:0;s:6:\"Maison\";}}}'),
