(20, 1, '2022-02-24 21:42:37', '2022-02-24 20:42:37', '', 'Travis Scott Splashed Out  Million On A Sleek Mansion - LA', 'Travis Scott has splashed out  million on a sleek mansion in Los Angeles, CA, USA on June 2020. The 28-year-old rapper paid the entire cost of the seven-bedroom property in Brentwood in CASH! It was originally put up for sale for a staggering  million last summer. His new three-floor estate, which is 16,7000 square feet, has 11 bedrooms. The massive rooftop includes a parking lot lined with foliage, and its driveway curves downward to become the third-floor balcony. Out in the backyard there is a long glass-bottomed infinity pool that offers breath-taking views of Los Angeles.\rAt one side of the swimming pool there is a gleaming hardwood deck lined with room for chairs and tables. Travis\' new backyard also includes a grassy area as well as a patio that spills into the living room on the second floor. One of the most eye-popping features of the house is a dizzying white spiral staircase against a grey metallic banister. Inside, theres also a gym, a games room and a home cinema complete with cushioned cinema-style seats that have cup-holders in the armrests. A huge bar has a gleaming black back wall lined with liquor shelves. Up on the third floor of his house, the hardwood flooring has a stylish three-dimensional cube pattern meant to look like tile. The master bedroom suite has a balcony and an ensuite bathroom with a luxurious bowl-shaped bathtub and a massive shower. A sitting room on the top floor has stunning city views with floor-to-ceiling windows. Travis has a two-year-old daughter called Stormi with his ex Kylie Jenner. The former couple still own a .5 million Los Angeles home. Photo by ABACAPRESS.COM  Maison Villa House  | 734262_031 Los Angekes Etats-Unis United States', 'inherit', 'open', 'closed', '', 'travis-scott-splashed-out-million-on-a-sleek-mansion-la', '', '', '2022-02-24 21:42:37', '2022-02-24 20:42:37', '', 8, 'http://local